  "description": {
    "zh": "接下来，你的任务是使用 M4A1 或一种俄式 AR-15 步枪，击杀几名 BEAR 和 Scav，记得装备 EOTech 光学瞄具。\n\n别忘了收集他们的狗牌，明白吗？\n\n完成任务后，你需要将使用的枪藏在海关地图的一个建筑物里。我觉得靠近 RUAF 路障的那个奇怪建筑不错——你们干员好像叫它“情报房”，对吧？真是个奇怪的名字……总之，把枪藏在二楼的图书室里。祝你好运！",
    "en": "So, for the next challenge you need to take out a few BEAR operators and bandits, and you need to use an M4A1 or one of these russian AR-15 rifles, it should also have an EOTech optic equipped.\nDon't forget to collect the dogtags, okay?\n\nAnyway, after you're done with that you need to hide the gun you used somewhere on customs, I was thinking about the weird building near the RUAF roadblock, I think you operators call it \"crackhouse\", right? What a weird name... Anyway, stash your gun somewhere in the library on the second floor, good luck."
  },
